column5: I know a few guys that SHOULD have these
Talk about setting the drag too tight!
do not let my girl friend find out about this

Do I need one?   Not anymore!  Ladies in hip waders aerializing 65ft of fly line or running down chrome steelhead in fast water has to be the hottest thing to look at out there…It wouldn’t be my fault either if they’re impressed with the size and action of my rod.
A Stripper Clause? ... That's pretty damn unfair.
To bad it wasn't this easy...
